author: AsapSCIENCE
description:
Pornography use has been increasing year on year around the world. This has led to a "crisis in male sexuality" by potentially increased erectile dysfunction in young men. On top of that, pornography use has been found to change the structure of your brain - changing all aspects of your life. Today we will explain the science of pornography, how it changes your brain, what to do about it and why it might be leading to erectile dysfunction.
